ropes just as it was, for Fredric Jameson, a form of politics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aLiterature (General). 4aGender Studies. 4aPhilosophy. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Semiotics & Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCOR eBook Package Archivez978311053617108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCOR eBook-Package 2016z978311066749340uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/9781501707001zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501707001zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781501707001.jpg  a978-3-11-053617-1 COR eBook Package Archive  a978-3-11-066749-3 COR eBook-Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA